Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Do Russians want Reagan out?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xcbn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Jan 1984
As the race for the White House begins in earnest, would the Soviets prefer to deal with someone other than Reagan? This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less